      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2004-07-22</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-11-10T16:37:22Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Play Fair at the Olympics Act - Amends Federal law relating to the United States Olympic Committee (USOC) to direct the USOC to require observance of certain labor standards by companies that enter into licensing agreements with it, and by subcontractors and suppliers of such companies.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
